commit.message: fix: pkg: remove "unbound variable" error in some matrix paths.
fix: pkg: cleaning unused code and variable. !minor
fix: pkg: python 3.7 is also incompatible with old ``pkg_resources``.
new: pkg: ``shtest`` is now an external test dependency.
new: pkg: update license years.
chg: dev: shtest output more columnised output
chg: doc: wrong spelling of "explicitly"
new: pkg: added explicit mention of status of coverage collection in ``bin/test``.

fix: dev: avoid DRY, use entrypoint !minor

And fixes coverage.
fix: pkg: test libyaml C implem in addition to python implem if available
chg: dev: added no coverage pragma to unused code. !minor

new: added ``-V|--version`` shyaml command line option to get full version information.

This includes ``shyaml``'s version, but also PyYAML version installed,
and availability of the C libyaml bindings, and if they are used.
chg: dev: usage doc syntax !minor
fix: document behavior on empty input
chg: dev: refactor out useless code double-check action identifier.
fix: dev: cosmetics !minor

fix: dev: correct the docstring of ``do(..)`` function.

It was incorrectly reporting the return type as string.
fix: doc: typo in os name !minor
new: python 3.7 compatibility
chg: dev: cosmetics !minor
new: support YAML streams (fixes #32)
chg: pkg: cosmetic indentation !minor

new: ``shyaml`` can now be used from within python.

You can import ``shyaml`` and launch inner function in a python
program thanks to accessible API.
fix: doc: typo when properly quoting ``\0`` !minor
new: ``-q`` or ``--quiet`` to avoid printing error message on missing paths. (fix #14)
chg: doc: finish to document all behaviors.
fix: doc: typo !minor
fix: pkg: ``appveyor`` doesn't support multiline commands.
new: pkg: full coverage support.

fix: dev: forcing display line-by-line in CI tools !minor

Must force flush of stdout's buffer after each success line.
